  "texts": [
    "In video-based corneal reflection, infrared light is projected onto the eyes and the light reflected off the cornea is tracked to estimate the position of the gaze.",
    "The fields of application were classified on the basis of information from other reviews (e.g., Suh and Prophet 2018; Zhao 2009).",
    "However, the classification was adapted to the needs of the papers found in this review.",
    "The fields are presented as follows:",
    "• Psychology: Experiences related to the study of human behavior, mental processes, and mental disorders."
  ]
}